00:56:15.990 --> 00:56:16.615 align:middle line:90%
HONG LIU: Yeah.

00:56:16.615 --> 00:56:18.480 align:middle line:84%
AUDIENCE: --which
factor do we give?

00:56:18.480 --> 00:56:19.500 align:middle line:90%
HONG LIU: Which factor?

00:56:19.500 --> 00:56:21.660 align:middle line:90%
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:56:21.660 --> 00:56:23.400 align:middle line:90%
HONG LIU: You mean--

00:56:23.400 --> 00:56:24.935 align:middle line:84%
we just use the
