in short ranged.

00:57:26.903 --> 00:57:27.570 align:middle line:90%
AUDIENCE: I see.

00:57:27.570 --> 00:57:27.990 align:middle line:90%
Oh.

00:57:27.990 --> 00:57:29.365 align:middle line:84%
HONG LIU: So the
weak interaction

00:57:29.365 --> 00:57:31.212 align:middle line:90%
