AUDIENCE: Got it.

00:57:31.920 --> 00:57:34.320 align:middle line:84%
HONG LIU: --but then
through the Higgs mechanism

00:57:34.320 --> 00:57:38.850 align:middle line:84%
and then the analog of A mu
for the weak interaction,

00:57:38.850 --> 00:57:40.950 align:middle line:84%
