becomes short ranged.

00:57:40.950 --> 00:57:41.410 align:middle line:90%
AUDIENCE: Got it.

00:57:41.410 --> 00:57:41.630 align:middle line:90%
That makes sense.

00:57:41.630 --> 00:57:42.780 align:middle line:90%
HONG LIU: Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:57:42.780 --> 00:57:43.890 align:middle line:90%
And yeah, yeah.

00:57:43.890 --> 00:57:45.190 align:middle line:90%
And yeah.

00:57:45.190 --> 00:57:45.690 align:middle line:90%
Good.

00:57:45.690 --> 00:57:46.860 align:middle line:90%
Other questions?

